# Admin Interface Structure

The plugin's admin interface is divided into tabs and managed by JavaScript modules.

## Main Template

The admin interface is defined in [admin-page.php](mdc:templates/admin-page.php) with these key sections:
- Import tab for uploading and processing files
- Log tab for viewing error logs
- Maintenance tab for cleanup operations

## JavaScript Components

JavaScript functionality is organized in modular files, loaded in sequence by [index.js](mdc:assets/js/admin/index.js):

### Core JavaScript Files

- [core.js](mdc:assets/js/admin/core.js) - Core utility functions
- [ui.js](mdc:assets/js/admin/ui.js) - Interface handling
- [ajax.js](mdc:assets/js/admin/ajax.js) - AJAX communication
- [tabs.js](mdc:assets/js/admin/tabs.js) - Tab navigation
- [preview.js](mdc:assets/js/admin/preview.js) - File preview functionality
- [import.js](mdc:assets/js/admin/import.js) - Import process management
- [log.js](mdc:assets/js/admin/log.js) - Log display handling
- [cleanup.js](mdc:assets/js/admin/cleanup.js) - Cleanup operations
- [main.js](mdc:assets/js/admin/main.js) - Final initialization
